snippet.title: Smelogs Playground - Trailer
snippet.description:
Smelogs Playground - Trailer 

JOIN OUR DISCORD for early playtest access! 👀
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/PZyhM94JSC

Wishlist on Epic Games Store! https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/smelogs-playground-a953e3
Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1799530/Smelogs_Playground/

Website: https://smelogsplayground.com/

Smelogs Playground is a Free-to-Play Real-Time Strategy game with charming aesthetics and a simple but effective gameplay mechanism. Take over the playful and rocky Smelogs to compete against each other for fun and honor!
